Class PrimitiveShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • mdraw.shapes.PrimitiveShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Shape
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Oval, Rect

    public abstract class PrimitiveShape
extends Object
implements Shape
    Base class for primitive shapes. PrimitiveShape defines position and width and height getHeight().
